{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1775867483988,"sessionID":"ses_2860db1f3ffeYXb6GNuqH407Xv","part":{"id":"prt_d79f3531b001UQmf1zxTS7W3i1","messageID":"msg_d79f3436e001sRpNfcuPLkmedA","sessionID":"ses_2860db1f3ffeYXb6GNuqH407Xv","type":"tool","tool":"read","callID":"toolu_6e3cc809900f4207b20e2db8","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"filePath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-MiniMax-M2.5_20260410T163134Z/changes/AR-027/delta-spec.md"},"output":"<path>/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-MiniMax-M2.5_20260410T163134Z/changes/AR-027/delta-spec.md</path>\n<type>file</type>\n<content>\n1: # Delta Spec: AR-027 ŌĆö SDK CodeInterpreterClient\n2: \n3: ## Overview\n4: \n5: <!-- Brief description of what this spec covers -->\n6: \n7: ## Base Specifications\n8: \n9: - **AR**: AR-027\n10: - **Module**: `sdk-python`\n11: - **Language**: Python\n12: - **Size**: M\n13: - **Base Specs**: <!-- Reference to base spec(s), e.g., sdk-python/spec.md -->\n14: \n15: ---\n16: \n17: ## Background\n18: \n19: <!-- Context and motivation for this change -->\n20: \n21: ---\n22: \n23: ## Requirements\n24: \n25: ### Requirement: <!-- Feature name -->\n26: \n27: The system SHALL <!-- description -->\n28: \n29: #### Scenario: <!-- Scenario name -->\n30: - **GIVEN** <!-- precondition -->\n31: - **WHEN** <!-- trigger -->\n32: - **THEN** <!-- expected outcome -->\n33: \n34: ---\n35: \n36: ## Acceptance Criteria\n37: \n38: 1. <!-- First acceptance criterion -->\n39: 2. <!-- Second acceptance criterion -->\n40: 3. <!-- Additional criteria as needed -->\n41: \n42: ---\n43: \n44: **End of Delta Spec AR-027**\n\n(End of file - total 44 lines)\n</content>","metadata":{"preview":"# Delta Spec: AR-027 ŌĆö SDK CodeInterpreterClient\n\n## Overview\n\n<!-- Brief description of what this spec covers -->\n\n## Base Specifications\n\n- **AR**: AR-027\n- **Module**: `sdk-python`\n- **Language**: Python\n- **Size**: M\n- **Base Specs**: <!-- Reference to base spec(s), e.g., sdk-python/spec.md -->\n\n---\n\n## Background\n\n<!-- Context and motivation for this change -->\n","truncated":false,"loaded":[]},"title":"workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-MiniMax-M2.5_20260410T163134Z/changes/AR-027/delta-spec.md","time":{"start":1775867483971,"end":1775867483986}}}}
